title: Onder Zee
overview: Onder Zee is a reality program that follows the life aboard a submarine of the Royal Dutch Navy. We will tag along for eight weeks in the Dutch submarine ''The Walrus'' under command of Captain Peters with a crew of 55 with nerves of steel. Submarines symbolize secret, invisibility and deadliness. They are used for a variety of missions including espionage, counterterrorism and anti-piracy.
